{"tid":1542251,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[真正搵仔]在台流亡手足手冊+支援","createTime":"2019-09-04T19:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T15:38:37.000Z","uid":314585,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"d663e47810bb920927ab3d541bda9ed0a479f7cd","tid":1542251,"uid":314585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T19:53:21.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟我唔多唔少去左台灣都有六載，話多唔多<br />\n有見及此，希望出一出POST，希望幫到手足，要去/已經去左<br />\n有好多好多長居台灣既手足係好願意幫手，香港亦有好多人會願意協助你地<br />\n希望你地睇到可以幫到你地,TG: paronday<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">-------------------------------分線-------------------------------------</span><br />\n係台灣，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目前難民法仲係處於難產階段</span></span></span>，你睇下書局老闆就知。<br />\n目前可以幫到你既有: <span style=\"color: red;\">30日旅遊簽(簡單自己網上搞)<br />\n半年探親簽(要去移民局搞，有錯請指正)^1，工作簽^2，移民^3。</span><br />\n^1  (應該係最好用，最大機會批)<br />\n香港澳門居民短期停留<span style=\"color: green;\">(已經係台灣既手足去移民局)</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">移民局位置:<a href=\"https://www.immigration.gov.tw/5385/5388/7181/7184/7193/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immigration.gov.tw%2F5385%2F5388%2F7181%2F7184%2F7193%2F&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6ruQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=913d26f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.immigration.gov.tw/5385/5388/7181/7184/7193/</a></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://coa.immigration.gov.tw/coa-frontend/overseas-honk-macao\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcoa.immigration.gov.tw%2Fcoa-frontend%2Foverseas-honk-macao&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6ruQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=17e04082\" target=\"_blank\">https://coa.immigration.gov.tw/coa-frontend/overseas-honk-macao</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">最近2年內拍攝之2吋半身彩色白底照片１張(照片規格請參考注意事項)，上傳相片檔案格式須為JPG或JPEG檔，相片圖檔檔案大小需在512KB以內。<br />\n香港永久性居民身分證、有效期3個月以上之香港護照或BNO護照、及回鄉證影本。<br />\n證照費：單次入出境證：新臺幣600元整；<del>一年多次入出境證：新臺幣1000元整；三年多次入出境證：新臺幣2000元整。</span></del></span><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要5工作天</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">VISA過左期既手足唔使怕快D搵手足幫手出境去日本沖繩，平過你返香港既機票!而且那霸有台灣經貿辦，可以申請上邊個隻半年簽。</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">快D加我TG，急死班手足啦出現啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去邊訓?(入邊有幾間旅館，唔使錢住，不過旅客唔該行開，幫左手足先)<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3214087/org/777da19ad69a9e3bb075050e1ef8f074.jpg/25PAXqIy3WKVm9Mv_u7N51fhXltviVrGLMIAQyzCAEM?v=w1280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3214087%2Forg%2F777da19ad69a9e3bb075050e1ef8f074.jpg%2F25PAXqIy3WKVm9Mv_u7N51fhXltviVrGLMIAQyzCAEM%3Fv%3Dw1280&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6ruQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=984a111a\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3214087/org/777da19ad69a9e3bb075050e1ef8f074.jpg/25PAXqIy3WKVm9Mv_u7N51fhXltviVrGLMIAQyzCAEM?v=w1280</a><br />\n私人推薦可以去:各大網吧，三溫暖(唔好去錯唔岩自己性向既)，台北車站。<br />\n不過如果真係無錢，快D去就近大學搵個間學校既僑生會/港澳會，通常佢地會有會社可能可以借俾你訓。<br />\n同埋台灣有好多香港人同埋熱心既台灣人，問佢地借宿都有可能OK。<br />\n話個數俾你知，台灣有8.9萬名逾期居留者[url](<a href=\"https://asean.thenewslens.com/article/111482\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasean.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F111482&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6ruQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=4b5532ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://asean.thenewslens.com/article/111482</a>)[/url]佢想搵你其實唔易嫁。<br />\n<br />\n電方面，台灣行110W，去地鐵站，火車站好多都有USB可以直接用。唔得就去5金鋪買個。7-11既唔好買，貴到HIHI<br />\n<br />\n工作方面:想知既推左我上去再講，我想幫到手足。<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------分線-------------------------------------------------<br />\n希望你地睇到可以幫到你地,TG: paronday<br />\n^2同^3唔係唔得，只係目前無咩時間打，有人想知再講。"},{"pid":"2e8748530a80b6d9ef1dcfddadd89ff42d1d8a39","tid":1542251,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T19:54:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ea445b93d54d3c9628db46ee56de297779bfe41","tid":1542251,"uid":259788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20